{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brew Besties is a couch co-op top-down game where 2-4 players have to brew potions and deliver them to impatient customers. Play through unique and interesting worlds, ranging from outer space,  gardens and frozen snowlands! Every world comes with unique obstacles that will challenge your teamwork. Get enough points and gather all three starts per stage to make you and your friends become the true Brew Besties</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this chaotic family game you need to work together to brew potions by helping each other prepare ingredients, managing the cauldron\u2019s fire, gathering firewood and reaching remote areas. Use your throwing ability to throw other players, whether to be helpful, or not, is up to you! But remember, both strategy and communication are essential for success.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A Thousand Grips","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772170/348a85325333eb15290c9da2c14532fe494c322c.jpg"},{"name":"Caution: Wet Floor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772170/6ca89740b9d12e1501ad5fc43a6f2ee8ae2fd168.jpg"},{"name":"The Pumpking","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772170/3d7fb33fb7cfa7e6ecd9a1098586da775395164c.jpg"},{"name":"Crystal Age","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772170/e04de1250a85d41a941e2cbfda99ee1792c16b06.jpg"},{"name":"Zen Achieved","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772170/e161c4d6b860abafe3ed6894d8b798ba1e41efab.jpg"},{"name":"I'm Freezing!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772170/c363ed8587fb7e24415f28a422899520f8b60fe7.jpg"},{"name":"I'm getting dizzy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772170/1e6f12083b709cc35e5daa41547a598